properties.Name: CustomerEducation
properties.Description:
The education attainment characteristics of the Individual Customer consisting of:

(1)  The Educational Institution attended
(2)  The Education Attainment Level at that institution
(3)  The Attendance Status
(4)  Defined for a period (Period Start Date/Period End Date)

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: EducationalInstitutionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Educational Institution.

Columns.Name: FieldOfStudyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Field of Study.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The Period Start Date for which the associated Individual Customer education attainment and characteristics are defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The Period End Date for which the associated Individual Customer education attainment and characteristics are defined.

Columns.Name: EducationAttainmentLevelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Education Attainment Level.

Columns.Name: StudentStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Attendance Status.

Columns.Name: CustomerEducationNote
Columns.Description: Notes regarding the associated Individual Customer education attainment and characteristics.
